OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMichael Sheen: I broke down
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhearing kids' care stories 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, How would you feel if your child, or   
OL,6, one you knew, was taken into care and  
OL,7, ended up living in a B&B, a hostel, or 
OL,8, even slept rough?                      
OL,10,FWhat I'm talking about here is "the    
OL,11,Fcare system", the safety net we'd rely 
OL,12,Fon if we couldn't look after our kids. 
OL,14,FI've been working on a BBC documentary 
OL,15,Fwhich has found teenagers are still    
OL,16,Fbeing placed in B&Bs and hostels - six 
OL,17,Fyears after the Welsh government said  
OL,18,Fit wanted to "eliminate" it.           
OL,20,FSome of the stories have shocked me.   
OL,23,D]G     From the BBC News Website       
